These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, satire
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, cricket
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, ship
1. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
2. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4
3. the person watching satire movies is the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | 7up  | almond-milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | superhero   |
| Sport         | cricket | badminton |
| Transport     | airplane | ship    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: cucumber, cauliflower
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, drama
2 different pets are kept: bird, fish
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, boat
1. the owner of the fish is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching mystery movies is the person driving the boat##1
3. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | cucumber     | cauliflower |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | mystery  |
| Pet           | fish         | bird     |
| Transport     | snowmobile   | boat    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite
The people have 2 different jobs:  pilot, writer
2 different pets are kept: dog, goat
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, motorbike
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the writer##3
2. the owner of the goat is on the right of the writer##1
3. the person drinking milk is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | sprite     | milk |
| Job         | writer | pilot    |
| Pet         | dog         | goat        |
| Transport   | roller         | motorbike    |

