.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, lemonade
There 2 different types of food: carrot, spinach
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, puzzles
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, indie
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the fan of indie is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | coffee |
| Food          | spinach   | carrot  |
| Hobby         | skydiving | puzzles     |
| Music-Genre   | d&b  | indie         |

