.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  lawyer, musician
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, malaysian
2 different pets are kept: ferret, snake
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in an even position##4
2. the malaysian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the musician is the australian##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | musician | lawyer    |
| Nationality   | australian       | malaysian |
| Pet           | ferret         | snake    |
| Sport         | cricket    | tennis   |

